title: 00165 no boot
message:
got a water damaged 00165 that has fanspin but does not boot.

cpu vcore - 1.7v
ppbus - 8.6

what other lines do you need?  I'm completely lost with this one.  is this damaged cpu?

title: 00165 no boot
message:
PLT_RESET_L pulsing?
Did you try to start in SMC bypass mode?

Check all SPI Bus Series Termination resistors and their traces.
Clean/remove J6100.
Try known good BIOS file.

title: 00165 no boot
message:
PLT_RESET_L pulsing?  - 0v not pulsing
Did you try to start in SMC bypass mode?  - yes no difference
j6100 - is very clean
Check all SPI Bus Series Termination resistors and their traces.  - checked all traces and everything looks good.  only trace i found was broken was to r5177, repaired that one and no change 

Try known good BIOS file. - can you help me with that?  i can take it off and download the dump, but could you clean it?

title: 00165 no boot
message:
